Welcome to Our Privacy Policy ‘’Your Privacy is important to us’’. Our privacy policy explains what info our Games collects when you visit our site or interact with our aps and games, as well as ways we might use or share it.
We’re highly serious in protecting the privacy rights of our users (“users” or “you“). This Privacy Policy (the “Policy”) describes the ways we collect, store, use, and manage the information, including personal information, that you provide or we collect in connection with our websites, or any of our game provided on a mobile platform (for example, Apple’s iOS App Store, Google’s Play Store) (collectively, the “Service”). Please note that the scope of this Policy is limited to information collected or received by us through your use of the Service. We’re not responsible for the actions of third party people or companies, the content of their sites, the use of information you provide to them or any products or services they may offer. Any link to those sites or placements by those sites does not constitute our sponsorship of, or affiliation with, those people or companies.
By using the Service, you are expressing your agreement to this Policy and the processing of your data, including your personal information, in the manner provided in this Policy. If you do not agree to these terms, please do not use the Service.
Collection & Use of User Information:
We collects information as described below. Our’s primary goals in collecting and using information is to create your account, provide Services to you, improve our Service, contact you, conduct research and create reports for internal use.
Customer Service:
We may collect your email address when you contact our customer service group and we may use that email address to contact you about your gaming experience with our games and notify you about company news and promotions.
Game Data Collection:
Whenever you play our games, we may collect data about all of your interactions with the game and with the other players inside the game via server log files.
Games Sites:
While you are browsing Our Site, your computer’s or any other device’s operating system, Internet Protocol (IP) address, access times, browser type and language and referring Web site addresses may be logged automatically. We may use this information to monitor and analyze your use of the Service. In addition, we may ask you to submit and we may process data that is personal to you, including but not limited to your name, profile photo, gender, age or birthday, links to your profiles on social networking websites and other third party sites, user names, e-mail and mail addresses. We may use this information to create a user profile. We may use your email address to contact you about your experience with our Sites and notify you about company news and promotions. Your gender and birthday may be used to analyze user trends and target certain promotions. Your mail address may be used if we have merchandise or other physical promotional materials that we want to send to you.
